<h2>Simple app for<br>healthcare workers</h2>
<p>An <a href="https://medium.com/simple-dot-org/simple-wins-best-in-show-at-the-ixda-awards-in-milan-a1c3a30a7d30">award-winning</a> Android app for healthcare workers to manage their patients with high blood pressure.</p>
<p>At every visit, a healthcare worker records the patient's BP and medicines, to create a useful longitudinal record for patient care <i>and</i> to monitor an NCD program overall.</p>

