<h3>What's special about Simple?</h3>
      <p>Simple is free, fast, easy to learn, and quick to deploy:</p>
      <div class="howitworks howitworks-left">
        <a href="/images/screen-bp.png"><a href="/images/screen-bp.png"><img src="/images/screen-bp.png" alt=""></a></a>
        <div>
            <h5>Record a BP in under 20 sec</h5>
            <p>Simple is fast and fits into most workflows, so healthcare workers spend more time with patients and less time doing data entry. A healthcare worker can record a visit with BP and medications in less than 20 seconds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="howitworks howitworks-right">
        <a href="/images/screen-search.png"><img src="/images/screen-search.png" alt=""></a>
        <div>
            <h5>Easy to learn</h5>
            <p>Because it's so simple, healthcare workers can learn Simple in the field in less than 2 hours. We regularly train users on-location in hospitals to use Simple right away.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howitworks howitworks-left">
        <a href="/images/screen-summary.png"><img src="/images/screen-summary.png" alt=""></a>
        <div>
            <h5>BP history is simply displayed</h5>
            <p>A patient's BP history is displayed simply, so nurses and doctors can scan it in a busy care environment. We will add graphing of BPs soon.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="howitworks howitworks-right">
        <a href="/images/screen-schedule.png"><img src="/images/screen-schedule.png" alt=""></a>
        <div>
            <h5>Follow-up with every patient</h5>
            <p>It's very important for patients to return to the facility for treatment on a regular schedule. Scheduling follow-ups is easy and the patient will receive text message reminders to return to care.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howitworks howitworks-left">
        <a href="/images/screen-overdue.png"><img src="/images/screen-overdue.png" alt=""></a>
        <div>
            <h5>Remind overdue patients to return</h5>
            <p>If a patient misses their follow-up visit, Simple will add them to an easy-to-use overdue list. Any staff member can call the patient and Simple hides their phone number from the patient.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="howitworks howitworks-right">
        <a href="/images/screen-connection.png"><img src="/images/screen-connection.png" alt=""></a>
        <div>
